OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FEngland fans have accused Fifa of
OL,8,Fapplying "one rule for one and one
OL,9,Frule for another" after Jarell Quansah
OL,10,Fwas handed a two-match suspension
OL,11,Ffollowing his red card against Mexico.
OL,13,FSupporters on South Beach in Miami,
OL,14,Fwhere England face Norway in their
OL,15,FWorld Cup quarter-final, said they
OL,16,Faccepted Quansah deserved to miss the
OL,17,Fnext match but questioned why United
OL,18,FStates striker Folarin Balogun had his
OL,19,Fsuspension lifted earlier in the
OL,20,Ftournament.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FQuansah's tackle was deemed "serious
OL,8,Ffoul play" under Fifa's disciplinary
OL,9,Fcode and the governing body announced
OL,10,Fon Thursday he will serve an immediate
OL,11,Fsuspension, ruling him out of
OL,12,FSaturday's game and a possible semi-
OL,13,Ffinal against either Argentina or
OL,14,FSwitzerland.
OL,16,FEngland fan Paul Elleray, 61, from
OL,17,FBerkhamsted, Hertfordshire, said:
OL,18,F"Well, I think it's a bit duplicitous.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@JO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,F"It seems to be one rule for one and
OL,8,Fone rule for the other, so it is what
OL,9,Fit is.
OL,11,F"I think he's been sent off, so he
OL,12,Fdeserves to be out, but that didn't
OL,13,Fhappen elsewhere.
OL,15,F"But I think we'll be all right."
OL,17,FQuansah was dismissed after a VAR
OL,18,Freview of his challenge on Mexico's
OL,19,FJesus Gallardo during England's
OL,20,Fdramatic 3-2 last-16 victory in Mexico
OL,21,FCity.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FThe decision to impose a two-match
OL,8,Fsuspension has intensified scrutiny of
OL,9,FFifa's handling of Balogun's red card
OL,10,Ffor the United States earlier in the
OL,11,Ftournament.
OL,13,FBalogun had initially been suspended
OL,14,Fafter his dismissal against Bosnia and
OL,15,FHerzegovina, but Fifa's disciplinary
OL,16,Fcommittee later suspended the ban
OL,17,Ffollowing an intervention from US
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump, allowing the
OL,19,Fstriker to play in the hosts' last-16
OL,20,Fdefeat by Belgium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FGeorge Bier, 25, from London, said he
OL,8,Fbelieved the decision was fair despite
OL,9,Fthe controversy surrounding Balogun's
OL,10,Fsuspension.
OL,12,F"I think it's fair," he said.
OL,14,F"I think it would have been very dodgy
OL,15,Fif it got overturned after the Balogun
OL,16,Fsituation.
OL,18,F"So, back to normality. It's fine.
OL,19,FWe'll deal with it."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@TO]vD@AOUzD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
