OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FPaul Dubberley, 67, from Aldridge in
OL,8,Fthe West Midlands, felt the sanction
OL,9,Fwas excessive.
OL,11,F"It just kind of seems a little bit
OL,12,Fharsh, really," he said.
OL,14,F"Yes, it was a red card. Was it a two-
OL,15,Fgame one? I don't know.
OL,17,F"I personally think that, especially
OL,18,Fwith everything that's gone on, that
OL,19,Fit's a bit on the harsh side.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@OO]vD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
