PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,F"I don't think we should have got a
OL,8,Fbye, I think he should be suspended.
OL,10,F"But obviously, the non-suspension of
OL,11,Fthe American, it's just ludicrous to
OL,12,Fbe honest.
OL,14,F"There's no sense to it, and it's kind
OL,15,Fof just Fifa all over to be honest."
OL,17,FHis friend, Norman Bartlam, 68, from
OL,18,FBirmingham, joked: "I think we need
OL,19,FKeir Starmer to intervene ` I'm sure
OL,20,Fthat would have the desired effect.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUwD@dO]zD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
