OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,F"That would probably increase it to a
OL,8,Ffour-game ban."
OL,10,FThe controversy has also prompted some
OL,11,Fsupporters to question the standard of
OL,12,Fofficiating at the tournament.
OL,14,FMr Bier said: "The officiating has
OL,15,Fbeen a bit dodgy.
OL,17,F"I thought Argentina had a bit of a
OL,18,Fsuspicious ruling out... against
OL,19,FEgypt. I thought that Egypt's goal
OL,20,Fshould have stood.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@OO]vD@OOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
