OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783653540
OL,3,C'One rule for one and one rule for
OL,4,Canother' ` fans react to Quansah
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,F"But maybe Messi is bigger than the
OL,8,FWorld Cup, perhaps."
OL,10,FQuestioned on whether he thought the
OL,11,Fofficiating at the World Cup had been
OL,12,Fgood enough, Mr Bartlam said:
OL,13,F"Generally, but you do think the
OL,14,Freferees have been leant on by certain
OL,15,Fpeople."
OL,17,FThe Football Association is understood
OL,18,Fto have raised its concerns with Fifa
OL,19,Fearlier this week despite having no
OL,20,Fright of appeal against the red card
OL,21,Fitself.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@TO]uD@AOUwD@HO]
